xfce4-clipman &
albert &

xinput set-prop "ETPS/2 Elantech Touchpad" "libinput Tapping Enabled" 1
xinput set-prop "ETPS/2 Elantech Touchpad" "libinput Horizontal Scroll Enabled" 1
